annotationA: Probable methylmalonate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase [acylating], mitochondrial; Plays a role in valine and pyrimidine metabolism. Binds fatty acyl-CoA (By similarity); Belongs to the aldehyde dehydrogenase family
annotationB: Yippee interacting protein 2; acetyl-CoA C-acyltransferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: fatty acid beta-oxidation; Belongs to the thiolase family
